'''Angela Aquereburu''' (wavutse ku ya 11 Mutarama 1977) ni umwanditsi wa sinema, atunganya amafilime akaba n'umuyobozi wa firime<ref>https://afrique.lalibre.be/60452/angela-aquereburu-dans-mes-series-je-veux-montrer-une-afrique-qui-fait-rever/</ref>.

== Ubuzima ==
Aquereburu yavukiye muri [[Togo]] umubyeyi ukomoka muri [[Gwadelupe|Guadeloupe]]<ref>https://myafricainfos.com/togo-qui-est-angela-aquereburu/</ref> . Ashishikajwe n'ubuhanzi kuva akiri muto, yize muri Togo na Pointe-a-Pitre, Guadeloupe mbere yo kwimukira i Paris kwiga mu ishuri ry'ubucuruzi rya ESCP <ref>https://adweknow.com/entretien-angela-aquereburu-directrice-de-societe-de-production-yobo-studios/</ref>.  Yabonye impamyabumenyi y'ikirenga mu kwihangira imirimo.  Aquereburu yashakanye n'umukinnyi wa filime Jean-Luc Rabatel kandi akora mu bakozi imyaka myinshi<ref>https://www.jeuneafrique.com/664246/culture/angela-aquereburu-la-shonda-rhimes-togolaise/</ref>. Mu mwaka wa 2008, ubwo yari mu biruhuko muri Togo, yamenye ko kuri televiziyo hari amakinamico gusa, maze afatanije n’umugabo we bazana igitekerezo cyo gukurikiranya filimi yitwa motorcycle taxis.<ref>http://www.tv5monde.com/programmes/fr/programme-tv-les-maternelles-d-afrique-quelle-langue-parler-a-la-maison/58711/</ref>  Umwaka ukurikira, Aquereburu na Rabatel bimukiye i Lomé maze bashinga isosiyete ikora amajwi n'amashusho Yobo Studios<ref>https://www.programme-tv.net/biographie/371867-aquereburu-angela/</ref>.  Igitekerezo cyabo cyo kwerekana tagisi cyashingiweho kuri ''Zem'', mini-serie ya episode 26 yiminota itanu, ifatanije na Canal + Afrique.<ref>https://copainsdavant.linternaute.com/p/angela-aquereburu-779348</ref> 

Umushinga we ukurikira wari urukurikirane rugufi  rwa filimi ya ''Palabres''<ref>https://forbesafrique.com/angela-aquereburu-productrice-de-series-a-succes/</ref> .  Muri 2017, yatangije ''ibitaro IT'', bikemura ibibazo byabaturage nka malariya no kwera uruhu kandi byibanda ku mico Idriss na Tania<ref>http://africine.org/personne/angela-aquereburu/21843</ref>. Aquereburu yavuze ko yatewe inkunga n'inda ye ya kabiri yo gukora iki gitaramo. Grey's Anatomy yagize uruhare runini.  Yatsindiye igihembo cy'uruhererekane rwiza mu iserukiramuco rya Vues d'Afrique i Montreal<ref>https://www.filmaffinity.com/us/search.php?stype=director&sn&stext=Angela%20Aquereburu</ref>.<ref>https://africafilmproducers.org/membership/angela-aquereburu-3/</ref> 

